      <title>赞比亚将提高电价 115% 以支付进口费用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/zambia-to-raise-power-tariffs-by-115-to-pay-for-imports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[赞比亚能源监管机构批准了国有电力公司的请求，提高电价以支付进口电费。此前，一百多年来最严重的干旱袭击了水电站，导致水电站每天长时间停电。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/zambia-to-raise-power-tariffs-by-115-to-pay-for-imports</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 16:04:04 GMT</pubDate>
